data.description: Welcome Home to this move-in ready single level, situated in a highly desirable community. Open-concept layout, enhanced by soaring vaulted ceilings and strategically positioned fans, ensuring year-round comfort. The expansive master suite offers dual vanities and a generous walk-in closet. Enjoy the luxury of soft-close cabinetry and a dedicated laundry room for added convenience. Don't miss the oversized 3-car garage and extra attic storage, there's plenty of room here for everything, whether it be recreational gear, a personal workshop, or simply extra storage space. Large & fully fenced backyard is ready for summer evenings. Relax on the charming front porch and take advantage of convenient freeway access and nearby amenities. The neighborhood also offers a variety of social activities, including monthly food trucks and holiday festivities, fostering a vibrant community spirit. *Please note that some photos have been digitally staged to showcase the property's potential.
